      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que si $\\forall X \\in M_n (\\Qq)$ $\\det (A + X) = \\det (X)$ alors $A = 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall X \\in M_n (\\Qq)\\)</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det (A + X) = \\det (X)\\)</span> alors <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
