      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $B \\in M_n (\\Qq)$ telle que $\\forall X \\in M_n (\\Qq)$ $\\det (A + X) =\n \\det (B + X)$. Montrer que $A = B$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(B \\in M_n (\\Qq)\\)</span> telle que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall X \\in M_n (\\Qq)\\)</span> <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det (A + X) =\n \\det (B + X)\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = B\\)</span>.</p>\n"
